The change between testing with Walrus DNS and IP address in the s3cfg config file are as follows:

*IP address ENABLED Walrus*

{code}
host_base = 192.168.39.102:8773
host_bucket = 192.168.39.102:8773
{code}

*Walrus DNS Test*

{code}
host_base = walrus.euca-hasp.eucalyptus-systems.com:8773
host_bucket = walrus.euca-hasp.eucalyptus-systems.com:8773
{code}

*DNS Lookup*

{code}
euca-prod-1-82:s3cmd haroldspencerjr$ nslookup walrus.euca-hasp.eucalyptus-systems.com
Server:		10.1.1.254
